                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0123MKL">Läqay Kidāna Mǝḥrat / MKL</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1917" notAfter="1918">According to the colophon the Ms.
                        was completed in 1910 A.M. (= 1917/18 A.D.) during the reign of Queen
                        Zäwditu (r. 1916-30, crowned in 1917) and during the tenure of Metropolitan
                        Ṗeṭros (d. 1917).</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer is mentioned as the donor
                     in the colophon, on 144va, and in the
                     supplication formulas. His father Gabra Madḫǝn (87ra, 91vb, 93vb, 144va) and his mother Walatta Kidān (57va, 91vb) are also mentioned. 
 Other family
                     members are also mentioned in the colophon.</provenance></history>
